Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-¬≠filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Set in the future on a deadly remote planet, ‚ÄúBadlands‚Äù follows a young Predator outcast (played by newcomer Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi) who finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Elle Fanning) as he embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. snippet.title: Bhagwat Chapter 1: Raakshas | Official Trailer | A ZEE5 Original | Arshad W, Jitendra K | Pre 17 Oct
snippet.description:
"Inspector Vishwas Bhagwat, battling personal demons and his anger issues, investigates the case of missing girls. His journey intersects with Sameer, a charming man in love. What connects the two?

snippet.title: New Leagues & Battle Modes Explained in Clash of Clans
snippet.description:
In October Update of Clash of Clans Prepare for the massive Split Matchmaking + New League System update, which separates gameplay into a casual Battle Mode (for farming loot with no Trophies earned or lost) and a competitive Ranked Mode (a new seasonal tournament structure that incorporates all 34 Trophy Leagues). This system introduces weekly Trophy resets for lower leagues and monthly resets for the Legend League, along with a League Floor to guarantee a minimum rank based on your Town Hall level, new Hard Mode Modifiers for the highest leagues, and several new achievements to track your progress in this game-changing competitive environment.

snippet.title: Kaka - Heer (Official Video) | Waris Shah | Punjabi Trandional Song 2025
snippet.description:
Kaka Ji Records Presents Kaka Ji New Song "Heer"

Singer - Kaka 
Music - kaka
Lyrics- waris shah
Video director -Robby Singh Padda 
Mix Master -Stereo Shinobi
Female lead -Kavya thakur 
Assistant director - Jagteshwar thind,Gurlal benipal
line Production- sukhi Khattra.
Costumes stylist- Khwaish mehta
Makeup- Manisha makeover
Produced by - Raghbir Singh,Gurpreet Singh , Gurwinder Tiwana 
Project by -Sahejpal Singh Sidhu

Enjoy And Stay Connected With Artist || Kaka
https://www.instagram.com/kaka._.ji?igsh=MTJ5d3lobHFzZDQwcg==
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoBZjU5zDSWhlewGr3KJdrg

Ranjha aakhda khiaal na pawo mere, sapp sheeh fakeer da des keha.
Koonjan waang mamuliyaan des chhade, asaan zaat sifat te bhes keha.
Watan damaan de naal te zaat jogi, sanu saak kabeelrha khesh keha.
Jehra watan te jat wal dhiaan rakhe, duniyaan daar hai oh darvesh keha.


Main ikallrha gall na jaan‚Äôna haan, tusi dovein nanaan bharjaaiyan ni.
Malzadiyan waang banaa teri, payi baithi hain suram-salaaiyan ni.
Pair pakkarh fakeer de te de bhikhia, arhiyan kehiyan kawariye laiyan ni.
dhyann rab te rakh , na ho tatti, gusse hon na bhaliyan deeyaan jaaiyan ni.
Tainu shauk hai tinan da bhagparriye, jinnaan daachiyan bahar charaaiyan ni.
Waris Shah ohh sadaa hi jindde ne, jinnaan keetiyaan neik kamaaiyan ni.

Dil fikar ne gheriya band hoya, Ranjha jiu gotey lakh khai baitha.
Sathon hoonj dhuaan sir cha turia, kaale bagh vich dher machai baitha.
Akhiyan meet ke rab dhiaan dhar ke, chare taraf hai dhunrha laai baitha.
Waris Shah us waqt nu jhoorda ee, jis velrhe akhiyaan laai baitha.

Heer naike patt da pahin tewar, waali itar faleel malanwaudi hai.
Kanjal bhinne neinn apraadh lathe, dovey husan de kattak le dhaanwdi hai.
Ranjha vekh ke aakhda pari koi, ikke bhawein taan Heer siyaal hove.
Koi hoor ki mohni indraani, Heer hove taan saiyan de naal howe.
Waris Shah aayi chambrhi Ranjhane nu, jeha gadhe de gaale vich laal hoye.


Awull pairr pakkrhe itaqaak karke, fer naal kalejhe de lag gayi.
Nawan taor ajube da nazar aaya, vekho jal patang te agg gayi.
Kehi lag gayi chinaga jag gayi, khabar jag gayi vajj dharagh gayi.
Yaaro thaggan di rihuryi Heer jatti, muh lagadiyaan yaar nu thagg gayi.
Agge dhoonwaan dhukhendrha jogirhe da, utton phook ke jhugrhe agg gayi.
Yaar yaar da bagh vich mel hoya, gall aam mashhoor ho jag gayi.
Waris tarutiyan nu rabb melda ae, vekho kamle nu pari lag gayi.


Heer ho rukhsat Ranjhe yaar kolon, aakhe sahitiye mata pakaiye ni.
Mere waaste us ne lae tarale, kiven us di aas pujaiye ni.



Aggon raiba sairfaan boliyan ne, keha bhabiye ni matha kherhiya ee.
Nain shokh hoye rang chamak aaiya, koi jobne da khooh gediyaa ee.
Nain mast gallan teriyan laal hoyiyan, dukkan bhann choli vich teliyaan ni.
Kise hik teri naal hik jodi, pedu naal valoodran meliyan ni.
Teriyaan gallan te dandan de daarah disan, ajj sodhiyaan thakaran cheliyaan ni.
Ajj nahi iyaaliyan khabar ladhi, baghiyaarann ne roliyaan cheliyaan ni.


Parnehan da mainu asar hoya, rang jarad hoya ese waaste ni.
shhapan khubb gayiyan gallan meriyan te, daag laal peye ese waaste ni.
Katte jaande nu bhaj ke mili saan main, tainiyan dhilliyan ne ese waaste ni.
Runni athru dulle san mukhde te, khull gaye tatolrhey paasate ni.
Mudhi payi banere te vekhdi saan, pedu laal hoye ese waaste ni.
Surakhi hothaan di aape mai chuus layi, rang udd gaya ese waaste ni.
Katta ghuttiya vich galvakadi de, dukkan laal hoyiyan ese waaste ni.
Mere pedu nu katte ne thudd maari, laasaan bhakhlan diyan mere mass te ni.
Hor puchh waris main gharibni nu, ki aakhde lok muhasate ni.


#warisshahkalam #warisshah  #Heerwarisshah #tradionalsong #heertradionalsong kaka new song,kaka new song #HeerWarisShah #SufiLoveStory #PunjabiEpic #IshqHaqiqi #WarisShah #HeerRanjha #SufiPoetry #PunjabiCulture #ClassicLiterature #IslamicRomance #SufiKalam #NewKalam, #PunjabiKalam #KalamBabaBulheShah

Kaka Ji Records Presents Kaka Ji New Song "Heer"

Singer - Kaka 
Music - kaka
Lyrics- waris shah
Video director -Robby Singh Padda 
Mix Master -Stereo Shinobi
Female lead -Kavya thakur 
Assistant director - Jagteshwar thind,Gurlal benipal
line Production- sukhi Khattra.
Costumes stylist- Khwaish mehta
Makeup- Manisha makeover
Produced by - Raghbir Singh,Gurpreet Singh , Gurwinder Tiwana 
Project by -Sahejpal Singh Sidhu

Enjoy And Stay Connected With Artist || Kaka
https://www.instagram.com/kaka._.ji?igsh=MTJ5d3lobHFzZDQwcg==
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoBZjU5zDSWhlewGr3KJdrg

Ranjha aakhda khiaal na pawo mere, sapp sheeh fakeer da des keha.
Koonjan waang mamuliyaan des chhade, asaan zaat sifat te bhes keha.
Watan damaan de naal te zaat jogi, sanu saak kabeelrha khesh keha.
Jehra watan te jat wal dhiaan rakhe, duniyaan daar hai oh darvesh keha.


Main ikallrha gall na jaan‚Äôna haan, tusi dovein nanaan bharjaaiyan ni.
Malzadiyan waang banaa teri, payi baithi hain suram-salaaiyan ni.
Pair pakkarh fakeer de te de bhikhia, arhiyan kehiyan kawariye laiyan ni.
dhyann rab te rakh , na ho tatti, gusse hon na bhaliyan deeyaan jaaiyan ni.
Tainu shauk hai tinan da bhagparriye, jinnaan daachiyan bahar charaaiyan ni.
Waris Shah ohh sadaa hi jindde ne, jinnaan keetiyaan neik kamaaiyan ni.

Dil fikar ne gheriya band hoya, Ranjha jiu gotey lakh khai baitha.
Sathon hoonj dhuaan sir cha turia, kaale bagh vich dher machai baitha.
Akhiyan meet ke rab dhiaan dhar ke, chare taraf hai dhunrha laai baitha.
Waris Shah us waqt nu jhoorda ee, jis velrhe akhiyaan laai baitha.

Heer naike patt da pahin tewar, waali itar faleel malanwaudi hai.
Kanjal bhinne neinn apraadh lathe, dovey husan de kattak le dhaanwdi hai.
Ranjha vekh ke aakhda pari koi, ikke bhawein taan Heer siyaal hove.
Koi hoor ki mohni indraani, Heer hove taan saiyan de naal howe.
Waris Shah aayi chambrhi Ranjhane nu, jeha gadhe de gaale vich laal hoye.


Awull pairr pakkrhe itaqaak karke, fer naal kalejhe de lag gayi.
Nawan taor ajube da nazar aaya, vekho jal patang te agg gayi.
Kehi lag gayi chinaga jag gayi, khabar jag gayi vajj dharagh gayi.
Yaaro thaggan di rihuryi Heer jatti, muh lagadiyaan yaar nu thagg gayi.
Agge dhoonwaan dhukhendrha jogirhe da, utton phook ke jhugrhe agg gayi.
Yaar yaar da bagh vich mel hoya, gall aam mashhoor ho jag gayi.
Waris tarutiyan nu rabb melda ae, vekho kamle nu pari lag gayi.


Heer ho rukhsat Ranjhe yaar kolon, aakhe sahitiye mata pakaiye ni.
Mere waaste us ne lae tarale, kiven us di aas pujaiye ni.



Aggon raiba sairfaan boliyan ne, keha bhabiye ni matha kherhiya ee.
Nain shokh hoye rang chamak aaiya, koi jobne da khooh gediyaa ee.
Nain mast gallan teriyan laal hoyiyan, dukkan bhann choli vich teliyaan ni.
Kise hik teri naal hik jodi, pedu naal valoodran meliyan ni.
Teriyaan gallan te dandan de daarah disan, ajj sodhiyaan thakaran cheliyaan ni.
Ajj nahi iyaaliyan khabar ladhi, baghiyaarann ne roliyaan cheliyaan ni.


Parnehan da mainu asar hoya, rang jarad hoya ese waaste ni.
shhapan khubb gayiyan gallan meriyan te, daag laal peye ese waaste ni.
Katte jaande nu bhaj ke mili saan main, tainiyan dhilliyan ne ese waaste ni.
Runni athru dulle san mukhde te, khull gaye tatolrhey paasate ni.
Mudhi payi banere te vekhdi saan, pedu laal hoye ese waaste ni.
Surakhi hothaan di aape mai chuus layi, rang udd gaya ese waaste ni.
Katta ghuttiya vich galvakadi de, dukkan laal hoyiyan ese waaste ni.
Mere pedu nu katte ne thudd maari, laasaan bhakhlan diyan mere mass te ni.
Hor puchh waris main gharibni nu, ki aakhde lok muhasate ni.

snippet.title: Takkar (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Manish Gurjar, Fiza Choudhary | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Takkar (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Manish Gurjar, Fiza Choudhary | New Haryanvi Song 2025

Dollar Music presents new haryanvi song Takkar by Masoom Sharma & Ashu Twinkle ft. Manish Gurjar & Fiza Choudhary . Lyrics penned by Amar Karnawal. Music given by Pinna Music. Video by Mohan Betaab.


Song : Takkar
Singer : Masoom Sharma & Ashu Twinkle
Lyrics : Amar Karnawal
Starring : Manish Gurjar & Fiza Choudhary
Music : Pinna
Video : Mohan Betaab
Dop : Sushil Thind
AD : Vishal Kumar, Manjot Gill
Hair, Makeup : Honey Kalsi
Editor :  Somvir Parjapat
DI : Sahil Patter
Production : Rahul Sungroya
Costumes : Rampy Sharma
Still & Making : Jagmohan
Casting : Rekha Thakur
Design : Prince Pannu
Producer : Nvii Chhaniwala, Kapil Arora
Label : Dollar Music
Digital Partner : Bounce Digital
Online Promotions : GEET DIGITALS ( 9053553351 )
Reels Promotion : Reels Factory (82220 65686)
Special Thanks : Dheeraj Shayar, Prik Roast, Aman, Sethi, Tinku Chopra, Samii, Rahul Chahar

Lyrics : 
Na seeli denda hon laadle naal jigane ki,
Tere yaar ne kardi band bolti jaan zamane ki,
Re tere sir loga ke raule
Haande case luanda bole
Nyu te jada din koni reh ghee teri sakkar me ,
Goj me asle
Unme goli
Gundey gaadi me s boli
Gelya yaara ki s toli
Pcr se chakkar me
Re karde chale yar ujaad
Se thada asleya gela laad
R jisne chava de se paad
Aaj maari koi na takkar me

Shaitano ka raja hai tu
Duniya tujse khalti hai
Bhokaal khada ho jata hai 
Jab teri pistol chalti hai,
O maa ne gunda ni jaamya mai halaato ki galti hai
Par paschim se uttar bharat tak 
Tere yaar ki chalti hai,
R haale se delhi gudgama
Dekha Tera tama jhama
Kar rha kya t or drama
Haande kiske chakkar me
Goj me asle
Unme goli
Gundey gaadi me s boli
Gelya yaara ki s toli
Pcr se chakkar me
Re karde chale yar ujaad
Se thada asleya gela laad
R jisne chava de se paad
Aaj maari koi na takkar me

R kyukar chale se bulldojar
Chale yaar mere tu gujjar
Tere gela karnawalia
S jo badmasha ka tutor,
Hootar police k baaje ja se
Yaar tere peeke nache ja se
Hindi amar amar si sunke
Madam tu b maache ja se,
R honi nhi kise te rees
Yaar thari sunle aaj manish
Ghanta ki kadwa raakhi khees
Jo maane khud ne aakhar s
Goj me asle
Unme goli
Gundey gaadi me s boli
Gelya yaara ki s toli
Pcr se chakkar me
Re karde chale yar ujaad
Se thada asleya gela laad
R jisne chava de se paad
Aaj maari koi na takkar me
